original_title: Bronx: Westchester Avenue - St. Ann's Avenue
text:
575 and 577 Westchester Avenue (elevated thereon), at, and adjoining the N.E. corner of St. Ann's Avenue, showing two old frame buildings with stucco fronts. The elevated is that of the I.R.T. Pelham Bay Park subway line.
June 25, 1938.
P. L. Sperr
